org.biopax.ols.impl

Class AbstractTermLinker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.biopax.ols.impl.AbstractTermLinker
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TermPathBean, TermRelationshipBean

    public abstract class AbstractTermLinker
extends Object

    relationship between controlled vocabulary / ontology term

    we use subject/predicate/object but this could also be thought of as child/relationship-type/parent.

    the subject/predicate/object naming is better as we can think of the graph as composed of statements.

    we also treat the relationshiptypes / predicates as controlled terms in themselves; this is quite useful as a lot of systems (eg GO) will soon require ontologies of relationship types (eg subtle differences in the partOf relationship)
